%% Flujo de completar perfil y reservar servicio
%% Dominio: booking | Tipo: flowchart
flowchart TD
    start([Inicio]) --> checkProfile{¿Perfil completo?}
    checkProfile -->|Sí| showServices[Mostrar servicios]
    checkProfile -->|No| editProfile[Completar perfil]
    editProfile --> checkProfile
    showServices --> selectService[Seleccionar servicio]
    selectService --> confirmBooking[Confirmar reserva]
    confirmBooking --> finish([Fin])
